RECOGNIZE ONCE

@include.the.recognize.command

@include.the.recognize.method

  The `--once` option recognizes the first phrase in an audio stream,
  optimized for interactive use cases.

  The `--once+` option repeatedly recognizes phrases in an audio
  stream, optimized for non-interactive use cases.

USAGE: spx recognize [...] --once

EXAMPLES

  spx recognize --microphone --once
  spx recognize --file hello.wav --once+

SEE ALSO

  spx help recognize
  spx help recognize continuous
